Just days after the "Boyfriend" singer was photographed smoking what looked like marijuana in a California hotel room on Jan. 4, Bieber posted this touching photo on Twitter of himself greeting one of his young fans -- 7-year-old leukemia patient Millie Flamm. "Look at this bundle of joy... I love her" he tweeted. The teen heartthrob delayed the start of his Salt Lake City concert to spend time with Flamm at Primary Children's Medical Center, who was too sick to attend the show.
